    <string name="shuttle_help_title">Help</string>
    <string name="shuttle_help_lost_title">1. Finding Lost Items on the Shuttle Bus</string>
    <string name="shuttle_help_lost_content">To retrieve lost items on the shuttle bus, please call the shuttle bus office at 031–400–4412 or visit the office on the first floor of the Education Building behind the Haengbok Hall.</string>
    <string name="shuttle_help_time_title">2. Shuttle Bus Schedule Issues</string>
    <string name="shuttle_help_time_content">If you experience issues due to non-compliance with the shuttle bus schedule, please call the General Affairs and Personnel Team at 031–400–4406.</string>
    <string name="shuttle_help_stop_title">3. Shuttle Bus Stop Locations and First/Last Bus Times</string>
    <string name="shuttle_help_stop_content">You can check the shuttle bus stop locations and the first/last bus times by pressing the "Bus Stop Info" button at the bottom of the arrival information screen for each stop.</string>
    <string name="shuttle_help_via_title">4. Checking Shuttle Bus Stops Along the Route</string>
    <string name="shuttle_help_via_content">Click on the information for the shuttle bus you wish to take! You can check the stops along the route of that specific bus.</string>
    <string name="shuttle_help_departure_title">5. Checking Shuttle Bus Departure Times</string>
    <string name="shuttle_help_departure_content">Turn on switch above the shuttle bus information! This will show the departure times for that bus.</string>
